    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/55dae215c20e7cd5c7a47f913dd20594.poster.avif?t=1769514990\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/55dae215c20e7cd5c7a47f913dd20594.webm?t=1769514990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/55dae215c20e7cd5c7a47f913dd20594.mp4?t=1769514990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>建造、探索和征服。这个由程序生成的无限世界中充满了谜团，你可以发展自己的定居点，并且领导远征，对抗海盗王、龙和堕落的巫师。你会花很多时间在地下城中穿行，寻找宝藏和原材料来制作装备？还是会回应冒险的召唤，穿越海洋，寻找强大的敌人来考验自己的能力？招募具有特殊技能的定居者，并与他们一起开采各种各样的矿石，制作适合你自己游戏风格的装备，并建立一个繁荣的村庄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 既可以单人游玩，也可以合作游玩——或者建立一个专用服务器，与数百名其他玩家一起游玩。世界是无限的，可以适应你选择的所有模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/184fe3fa8f12c8b1ca065372ead20d99.poster.avif?t=1769514990\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/184fe3fa8f12c8b1ca065372ead20d99.webm?t=1769514990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/184fe3fa8f12c8b1ca065372ead20d99.mp4?t=1769514990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/9fca8baa45d927912826ff650580a968.webp?t=1769514990\" width=616 height=51 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从简陋的开端开始，发展自己的聚居地，建立果园、农场和工坊等设施。招募定居者，让他们在你的土地上工作，饲养动物，获取资源，这个过程不需要你的持续关注和监督。利用他们的专业知识来协助你准备下一次探险，定居者越多，你的聚居地实力就会变得越强。雇佣守卫并制造陷阱，抵御来自这个世界的各种危险。出售商品，用财富与邻近的聚居地进行贸易，提前获得可能会急需的设备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/7672e78ecaac33c241da36dfe8e2cc67.poster.avif?t=1769514990\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/7672e78ecaac33c241da36dfe8e2cc67.webm?t=1769514990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/7672e78ecaac33c241da36dfe8e2cc67.mp4?t=1769514990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/8995a58274891f47dee3e6dfa8aa0be6.webp?t=1769514990\" width=616 height=51 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是单人游玩，还是与几个朋友一起同乐，甚至是为数百名玩家创建一个专用服务器，《奈斯启示录》的世界及其中的威胁都能提供有意义的挑战。面对分布在各种生物群落中的独特怪物，既可以自由探索，也可以接受特定的任务。你会成为神射手弓兵，近战斗士，还是一名魔法技艺大师？你和朋友是会建立相互独立而又相互竞争的聚居地，还是会集中资源，分工明确，共同建立一个巨大的聚居地？面对强悍的 Boss 时，你是会组成一个经过精心平衡，具有强大协同作用的队伍，还是会努力独吞所有的荣耀？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/6410b898abc849eb42ff0a9fb3965e8c.poster.avif?t=1769514990\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/6410b898abc849eb42ff0a9fb3965e8c.webm?t=1769514990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/6410b898abc849eb42ff0a9fb3965e8c.mp4?t=1769514990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/83e799d7415ae06b21b3bf963821dd46.webp?t=1769514990\" width=616 height=51 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >砍伐树木，开采并加工矿石，采摘草药，搜刮被打败的怪物尸体，用这些资源来制作一切物品，从墙壁和家具，到盔甲、药剂、卷轴、饰品和武器。虽然某些独特装备只能通过击败特殊的敌人来获得，但其他的一切物品都可以通过多个工坊来制造，让你自己、来访的朋友和忠诚的定居者武装起来。解锁额外装备，获得新资源，还可以发现无数种制作、建造和游玩的方法。装备组合几乎无穷无尽，意味着总会有新东西等你尝试。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 随心游玩，自定义难度和多种游戏规则，满足自己的喜好。如果你不喜欢有入侵者出现在你的聚居地中，那就关掉相关选项，然后调整游戏规则，例如日夜循环的长度，或是 Boss 战的难度。从宠物鹦鹉、企鹅到精灵神灯、鸵鸟坐骑和独特服装，《奈斯启示录》有无数的选择等你探索。无论你是单人游戏还是和朋友一起玩，无论你想提高难度还是放松一下，每一次历程都是一个机会，可以让你编织不同于以往的史诗故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/7566a3eaeda4e27200fc22a11ac66a1b.poster.avif?t=1769514990\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/7566a3eaeda4e27200fc22a11ac66a1b.webm?t=1769514990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1169040/extras/7566a3eaeda4e27200fc22a11ac66a1b.mp4?t=1769514990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
